block content
  h1 Installed apps
  ul
    for app in apps
      li
        a(href="/apps/#{app.uniqueId}/")= app.name
        |  - is running?
        if app.running
          |  yes
        else
          |  no
        |  - is enabled?
        if app.enabled
          |  yes
        else
          |  no

  p
    a(href="/apps/create/") Create new app